{"tid":1309754,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手主人] 主子要轉貓糧，求專業意見","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:41:58.000Z","uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e63534c937b117cf8ade5c5752d444952dda9723","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"主子係異短，宜家一歲兩個月大，佢細細粒食極唔肥，一月頭睇獸醫得1.73kg, 而且腸胃好敏感，轉過一次糧 溝一半比佢食，柯到七彩，果排連食雞柳都柯，所以我即刻換番舊糧比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家食緊隻糧係日本牌子，Beauty pro 子貓用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排上網了解緊轉咩糧好，但係唔知轉邊款比較好，而且唔係預算好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位貓奴指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食緊呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jk4U92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jk4U92.png&h=75c1540c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6jhvJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6jhvJp.png&h=67c08671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d680781fdc512bb78bcff1b634ee43c7dbaefa60","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"係屋企附近間x-pets度買左包細貓糧，我見佢係Grain free/sans grains, 好似係對主子好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問埋如果我要睇成份揀貓乾糧，除左要低碳水化合物，要係用新鮮肉做，仲有咩要留意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0r5TOxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0r5TOxu.png&h=ddca7c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cn5Mo5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcn5Mo5Q.png&h=601afc1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d322558d3118beb9c3c744c9035b5c58b918923","tid":1309754,"uid":218141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d10e5c278d3655f8202ef2988349d120676f2529","tid":1309754,"uid":7468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"轉糧唔可以一轉轉一半進取<br />\n要好慢好慢咁轉，十分一十分一咁慢慢加上去"},{"pid":"abe66150da4557288268fc53ee79ed97d8cfa810","tid":1309754,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"食緊呢隻<br />\n無穀物既<br />\n當貓黎講 穀物係對佢地身體唔好既成份<br />\n<br />\n但呢隻比較貴<br />\n$250幾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XHiZNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XHiZNr.jpg&h=e604253a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff3974c837053acb0399d3f486aece07df12fa57","tid":1309754,"uid":273989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"轉糧要慢慢試<br />\n最好睇獸醫，如果有需要寧願食處方糧（處方乾乾唔係好貴），等佢穩定d先轉番其他<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：主子係敏感底，由乾乾轉左食全濕"},{"pid":"509d38d75ab6ee89f4e9dcdd411ad9dd7a45f9cc","tid":1309754,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"ziwipeak k9<br />\n利伸全濕"},{"pid":"253df51b8489198160a8860f3088108c1be9c0b6","tid":1309754,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"你認真？<br />\n我隻異短4個月個陣體重同你個隻已經一樣<br />\n1歲2個月英短唔多食野都有3.5kg<br />\n你個隻可能營養不良喎"},{"pid":"02f549ad6dbe6895885b10895c8713d93fcc7aa3","tid":1309754,"uid":43720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"可以試下wellness呀<br />\n唔算好貴，但營養唔會差得過d貴價糧"},{"pid":"86ad8da17de95f1cea12215ac223579f9d00b6a4","tid":1309754,"uid":176272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<br />\n最新白宮聯署！要求美國國會立即通過《香港人權民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUylDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=ed3a0d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n刻不容緩，立即簽名要求美國國會通過！"},{"pid":"0651f469cb93fdaf682acd3ff09a94194a5d56a4","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253df51b8489198160a8860f3088108c1be9c0b6","tid":1309754,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"你認真？<br />\n我隻異短4個月個陣體重同你個隻已經一樣<br />\n1歲2個月英短唔多食野都有3.5kg<br />\n你個隻可能營養不良喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"真架... 唉，果時比隻貓我果個人話 唔可以餵咁多比佢食，一日兩餐每餐食小小就夠，後尾我見佢食極都唔肥就覺得怪，之後放長糧比佢。可惜都係食唔肥"},{"pid":"58eb6211a2748d68a57625f61e2e4b023e02dc70","tid":1309754,"uid":31571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0651f469cb93fdaf682acd3ff09a94194a5d56a4","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253df51b8489198160a8860f3088108c1be9c0b6","tid":1309754,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"你認真？<br />\n我隻異短4個月個陣體重同你個隻已經一樣<br />\n1歲2個月英短唔多食野都有3.5kg<br />\n你個隻可能營養不良喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"真架... 唉，果時比隻貓我果個人話 唔可以餵咁多比佢食，一日兩餐每餐食小小就夠，後尾我見佢食極都唔肥就覺得怪，之後放長糧比佢。可惜都係食唔肥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:11:35.000Z","msg":"你隻貓 似要食罐罐吸收多啲 <br />\n我初養都俾獸醫話 too skinny<br />\n話要食多啲罐罐 吸收多啲<br />\n同埋佢食得少野 可能都會飲水少<br />\n如果你開始俾罐 最好都倒啲水溝埋一齊等佢一次過飲 同 食多啲"},{"pid":"d5c1a5fdd69d3bfe66cc6dbff599dbcbc6eb4380","tid":1309754,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"餵下益生菌先<br />\n我五隻貓都冇敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542f18bced0fc40af916c48661a139fefcbb7608","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c1a5fdd69d3bfe66cc6dbff599dbcbc6eb4380","tid":1309754,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"餵下益生菌先<br />\n我五隻貓都冇敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"多謝分享，但有無牌子可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b08fea66604e7583f9e40558f7a99b37ada109","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58eb6211a2748d68a57625f61e2e4b023e02dc70","tid":1309754,"uid":31571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0651f469cb93fdaf682acd3ff09a94194a5d56a4","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253df51b8489198160a8860f3088108c1be9c0b6","tid":1309754,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"你認真？<br />\n我隻異短4個月個陣體重同你個隻已經一樣<br />\n1歲2個月英短唔多食野都有3.5kg<br />\n你個隻可能營養不良喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"真架... 唉，果時比隻貓我果個人話 唔可以餵咁多比佢食，一日兩餐每餐食小小就夠，後尾我見佢食極都唔肥就覺得怪，之後放長糧比佢。可惜都係食唔肥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:11:35.000Z","msg":"你隻貓 似要食罐罐吸收多啲 <br />\n我初養都俾獸醫話 too skinny<br />\n話要食多啲罐罐 吸收多啲<br />\n同埋佢食得少野 可能都會飲水少<br />\n如果你開始俾罐 最好都倒啲水溝埋一齊等佢一次過飲 同 食多啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"我試過罐罐溝浸濕左嘅糧比佢食，柯到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔知佢有咩係食得，有咩唔食得..."},{"pid":"f34192ae63842295958415307bf51b3a84cd41fc","tid":1309754,"uid":19087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"樓主，如果喂 Grain Free 要小心啲<br />\n最近美國 FDA 出咗報告調查講 Grain Free Diet 同擴張型心肌病 （dilated cardiomyopathy) 有好大關聯，但係仲未搵到個 exact cause。 <br />\n個報告嘅更新時間係：June 27, 2019<br />\n<br />\n主要係英文，但你可以睇下有啲咩 Brands 係比人 Reported 得最多嘅<br />\n（雖然個報告主要係講狗，但係貓都有）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fda.gov/animal-veterinary/news-events/fda-investigation-potential-link-between-certain-diets-and-canine-dilated-cardiomyopathy?fbclid=IwAR3LTxIdTFAvYmAnNxqOwH_7q8AI_097DpLVYNLTt4M3n18rZ5bkoiQxzyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fanimal-veterinary%2Fnews-events%2Ffda-investigation-potential-link-between-certain-diets-and-canine-dilated-cardiomyopathy%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3LTxIdTFAvYmAnNxqOwH_7q8AI_097DpLVYNLTt4M3n18rZ5bkoiQxzyc&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUylDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=021c1b58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fda.gov/animal-veterinary/news-events/fda-investigation-potential-link-between-certain-diets-and-canine-dilated-cardiomyopathy?fbclid=IwAR3LTxIdTFAvYmAnNxqOwH_7q8AI_097DpLVYNLTt4M3n18rZ5bkoiQxzyc</a><br />\n<br />\n另外個人建議係，如果見到啲糧嘅成份寫住 &quot;by product&quot;, &quot;meal&quot;，等等嘅字眼就唔好買。同埋留意下有 legumes 嘅成份 (peas, lentils, beans, etc.) 都要小心啲。<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係專業"},{"pid":"068d03ce50c132350b57eb679094674e2827041a","tid":1309754,"uid":81333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"咁敏感最好轉凍乾生肉糧<br />\n一來肉成份多，二來貓貓食生肉易d吸收<br />\n<br />\n初初我就唔建議你比血淋淋既生肉啦，比較麻煩<br />\n凍乾其實都係生肉，但好似乾糧咁係一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食果陣加水，浸淋左比佢食就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係就係貴少少，但好多腸胃敏感貓食完都即刻好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉既話，比新糧前餓12個鐘、等佢個肚空哂先，呢個時候食凍乾生肉就最易吸收同消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牌子好多：k9，汪喵，primal ...<br />\nZiwipeak 就唔洗加水好似乾糧咁比，仲方便，不過前提係你make sure 你貓貓夠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f905fcc1d441cb7dee5dc518f7585c4dd7f3db","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068d03ce50c132350b57eb679094674e2827041a","tid":1309754,"uid":81333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"咁敏感最好轉凍乾生肉糧<br />\n一來肉成份多，二來貓貓食生肉易d吸收<br />\n<br />\n初初我就唔建議你比血淋淋既生肉啦，比較麻煩<br />\n凍乾其實都係生肉，但好似乾糧咁係一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食果陣加水，浸淋左比佢食就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係就係貴少少，但好多腸胃敏感貓食完都即刻好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉既話，比新糧前餓12個鐘、等佢個肚空哂先，呢個時候食凍乾生肉就最易吸收同消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牌子好多：k9，汪喵，primal ...<br />\nZiwipeak 就唔洗加水好似乾糧咁比，仲方便，不過前提係你make sure 你貓貓夠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"好啊好啊～～謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d4dfce3653427fad210041dfbff258392f86ab","tid":1309754,"uid":157592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"試下益生菌？ 但我果隻係狗狗 都係比多小小野就柯 仲要瘦 食左益生菌冇再柯"},{"pid":"eabf43748054834f3ee4637640244c6d6377eb5d","tid":1309754,"uid":92906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"兩隻主子食左幾年now無穀物<br />\n果時老婆比較左好多隻至決定<br />\n可以睇睇"},{"pid":"b8d3aa32414b441d2c5465cad61df330fc29811d","tid":1309754,"uid":148853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d4dfce3653427fad210041dfbff258392f86ab"